Palma Grey Corner Rattan Casual Garden Dining and Lounge Set 9 Seater
products.description: Transform your outdoor living space with the Palma Rattan Corner Sofa Lounge Set. Perfect for lounging and al fresco dining, this 9-seater rattan garden furniture ensemble features an outdoor corner sofa, a dining table, and versatile stools, making it a stylish and functional addition to your garden. What it includes: 7-seater corner rattan sofa: Two modular sections measuring L.200 x D.74 x H.82.5cm and L.207 x D.74 x H.82.5cm. 1 rectangular dining table: With a tempered glass top, measuring L.150 x W.80 x H.65cm. 1 square stool: Measuring L.44 x W.44 x H.41cm. 1 rectangular stool: Measuring L.100 x W.44 x H.41cm. Luxuriously thick removable grey cushions for ultimate comfort. The design file: Materials: Crafted from high-quality polyrattan on a powder-coated steel frame, this set is built to last. Durability: Weather-resistant and low maintenance, it’s designed for longevity and easy care. Aesthetic: The sleek grey rattan and plush cushions add a touch of luxury to any garden space. The key information: Dimensions: Sofa: L.200/207 x D.74 x H.82.5cm. Table: L.150 x W.80 x H.65cm. Square Stool: L.44 x W.44 x H.41cm. Rectangular Stool: L.100 x W.44 x H.41cm. Comfort: Removable seat and back cushions for added convenience and easy cleaning. Seating Capacity: Comfortably seats up to nine people, perfect for gatherings. Enhance your outdoor experience: Optional extras: Pair the set with a sun lounger, covers, heaters, and parasols from our exclusive Palma outdoor furniture bundles. Protection: Keep your set clean and dry with the made-to-measure Palma furniture cover. Storage: Use the Palma cushion storage box to store your cushions safely and keep them dry all year round.

products.product_title: Gigi 5 Seater Teak Garden Sofa and Armchair Set
products.description: Gigi combines a strong and bold silhouette with the softness of a teak construction that creates a timeless and organic feel. Wide and spacious armchairs and a generously proportioned corner sofa allow you to lounge in luxury, while the cushions are also stain resistant and UV resistant.

products.product_title: Havana Dark Grey 8 Seater Aluminium and Textilline Patio Dining Set
products.description: Enjoy sleek, modern outdoor dining every time. Our Havana 8 Seater Aluminium Patio Dining Set gives you all the excuses you need to take dinnertime outside. It’s crafted from highly robust aluminium which is powder coated for a sleek finish which prolongs and protects its appearance. Better still, we made sure Havana’s chairs are made with comfort in mind. A soft and breathable textiline back and seat delivers comfort and support, so your dinner conversations can continue long into the evening.

products.product_title: Ion 4 Seater Teak and Aluminium Garden Sofa and Armchair Set
products.description: No sharp edges in sight. That was the brief when we designed Ion, a 4-seater garden that combines a 2-seater sofa and two matching armchairs. You’ll find curved lines throughout, giving a natural and organic feel that’s harmonious with your outdoor space. Why have one coffee table when you can have two? Pair them together for a layered feel or separate them so they’re within easy reach.

products.product_title: Kiki 2 Seater Beige Aluminium Outdoor Sofa
products.description: Keeping it simple never looked so elegant- Kiki is our classic 2-seater garden sofa that gives you all of the sophistication of her indoor counterparts. The difference? UV resistant olefin cushions and an ultra-hardwearing aluminium frame that’s suitably qualified for life in your outdoor space. Kiki’s neutral sand-coloured cushions will suit any garden, while her armless design gives an effortlessly modern feel.

products.product_title: Kiki Beige 3-Seater Organic Garden Chaise Sofa
products.description: Our Kiki 3-seater chaise sofa adds understated elegance to your outdoor space. Its curved silhouette creates a natural and organic feel that gives you the sophistication of indoor furniture for your outdoor space. Thick and chunky olefin cushions deliver superior comfort, while a slim aluminium frame in a matching ‘sand’ colour gives the Kiki chaise durability you can rely on.

products.product_title: Lima 7 Seater Rattan Grey Garden Sofa Set With Sools and Up-Down Table
products.description: Like the relaxed look of a low coffee table but want the practicality of a dining set? Our Lima Up-down set proves you really can have it all. Our most versatile design yet, it’s easily adjustable, so you can switch from uninterrupted lounging to al fresco dining in seconds. Plus, it includes plenty of the features you’ll find across our collection, such as easily removable cushions with indoor-quality comfort. Not convinced yet? Did we mention this corner sofa set is maintenance-free? All you need to do is sit back and relax.

products.product_title: Lima 5 Seater Rattan Grey Sofa and Armchair Garden Furniture Set
products.description: Create a social and inviting outdoor space with our Lima 5 Seater Sofa and Armchair Set. This polyrattan garden furniture set lets you replicate the intimate feel of your indoor seating area and configure a layout that suits your space. Place the sofa and armchairs opposite on another, or split the armchairs either side of the sofa- Lima works for whatever space you have. One thing’s for sure, the glass-topped coffee table makes the perfect place to rest your drink. Plus, you’ll be sitting comfortably in our signature ultra-chunky seat and back cushion.

products.product_title: Linh 6 Seater Corner Acacia Wood Garden Sofa Set
products.description: Inspired by luxury resorts, Linh delivers five star quality, comfort and style. This expertly crafted corner sofa combines light-toned acacia wood with thick and bouncy olefin seat and back cushions, so you can create a haven of relaxation.

products.product_title: Chesterton Grey 5 Seater Corner Rattan Garden Sofa Lounge Set
products.description: Where practicality meets style, the Chesterton Corner Lounge Set is proportioned for everyday use within the family home.
